# Documentation backpressure

A task is **not complete** until living docs under `docs/` match the change. Templates are copy-only.

**Templates:** `docs/frontend/context/TEMPLATE.md`, `docs/backend/context/TEMPLATE.md`, `docs/adr/template.md`, `docs/frontend/specs/TEMPLATE.md`, `docs/backend/specs/TEMPLATE.md`

**Index:** [docs/README.md](../../docs/README.md). Root keeps only `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md` (stubs), and `.cursor/`.

## After every code or behavior change

| Change type | Update |
|-------------|--------|
| Edits under `frontend/src/app/` | [docs/frontend/context/app.md](../../docs/frontend/context/app.md) |
| Edits under `frontend/assets/` | [docs/frontend/context/assets.md](../../docs/frontend/context/assets.md) |
| Edits under `frontend/src/components/` | [docs/frontend/context/components.md](../../docs/frontend/context/components.md) |
| Edits under `frontend/src/hooks/` or `frontend/src/constants/` | `docs/frontend/context/<scope>.md` if that scope file exists |
| New domain term or role | [docs/frontend/context/project.md](../../docs/frontend/context/project.md) → Ontology |
| Local design choice | relevant `docs/frontend/context/*.md` → Decisions |
| Code pattern change | relevant `docs/frontend/context/*.md` → Patterns |
| New hard rule | relevant `docs/frontend/context/*.md` → Policies |
| Shipped feature with spec | matching `docs/frontend/specs/*.md` or `docs/backend/specs/*.md` — check ACs |
| Architecture decision | `docs/adr/ADR-NNN-*.md` + [overview.md](../../docs/adr/overview.md) |
| Backend domain work | matching `docs/backend/context/*.md` |
| Completed planned work | [implementation-plan.md](../../docs/implementation-plan.md) |
| End of session | [progress.md](../../docs/progress.md) |
| User-visible capability changed | [current.md](../../docs/current.md) |
| Brand, UI tokens, or copy tone | [brand.md](../../docs/frontend/brand.md) |
| Org account access (no secrets in repo) | [accounts-and-access.md](../../docs/accounts-and-access.md) |
| Agent commands or repo layout | [agents/AGENTS.md](../../docs/agents/AGENTS.md) |
| Product vision or setup | root `README.md` only |

## Verification before “done”

```bash
cd frontend && npx tsc --noEmit
npm run lint # when relevant
npm test # when relevant
```

## When unsure

- Spec exists? Check off ACs in `docs/*/specs/` before claiming done.
- Architectural? ADR + link from [project.md](../../docs/frontend/context/project.md).
- What runs today changed? Update [current.md](../../docs/current.md).
